## Who is MediScan AI for?
MediScan AI is designed for:
- 🏥 Small clinics and rural doctors without access to specialists
- 🧑‍⚕️ General physicians needing a quick second opinion
- 🔬 Medical students and researchers
- 🏫 Medical colleges as a teaching tool

> ⚠️ Note: This tool requires proper medical images — dermoscopy 
> images for skin, chest X-rays for pneumonia, and fundus camera 
> images for eye diseases. It is not designed for casual smartphone 
> photos and should not replace professional medical advice.
